code: @TaskAction public void runJarHellCheck() {     LoggedExec.javaexec(getProject(), spec -> {         spec.classpath(getClasspath()).         spec.executable(getJavaHome() + "/bin/java").         spec.setMain("org.elasticsearch.bootstrap.JarHell").     }). }
public void setJavaHome(Object javaHome) {     this.javaHome = javaHome. }
@Classpath public FileCollection getClasspath() {     return classpath.filter(file -> file.exists()). }
public void setClasspath(FileCollection classpath) {     this.classpath = classpath. }
